The Big Tariffs are hereBiden just slapped a 100% tax on Chinese car imports. Here's what that will and won't accomplish. https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-big-tariffs-are-here https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/the-big-tariffs-are-hereNoah Smith Tue, 14 May 2024 08:03:35 GMT <div class="captioned-image-container"><figure> <a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg" width="696" height="618.7700534759358" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:665,&quot;width&quot;:748,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:696,&quot;bytes&quot;:41259,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F8dfd279f-f88e-4367-a21e-3616105ec1e5_748x665.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture></div></a> <polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line><figcaption class="image-caption">照片由<a href="https://unsplash.com/@veverkolog?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Dušan veverkolog</a>在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/gray-concrete-building-XlNcs-6SkS0?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上拍摄</figcaption></figure></div><p>乔·拜登即将对中国制造的电动汽车<a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/biden-to-announce-new-100-tariffs-on-chinese-evs/">征收100%的关税</a>（更新：关税<a href="https://www.whitehouse.gov/briefing-room/statements-releases/2024/05/14/fact-sheet-president-biden-takes-action-to-protect-american-workers-and-businesses-from-chinas-unfair-trade-practices/">现已公布</a>，其中还包括半导体、钢铁和铝、港口起重机、太阳能电池板和医疗产品）。</p><p> 100%的关税绝对是<em>巨额</em>关税。这意味着中国电动汽车制造商必须以其他地方生产的电动汽车一半的价格在美国销售电动汽车才能保持竞争力。那是不会发生的。</p><p> 100% 的关税可能足以将基本上<em>所有</em>中国制造的电动汽车拒之门外。荣鼎集团最近发布了一份名为“<a href="https://rhg.com/research/aint-no-duty-high-enough/">关税还不够高</a>”的报告，认为欧洲将需要 40-50将中国电动汽车拒之门外的关税百分比：</p><blockquote><p>欧盟委员会可能在未来几个月内对从中国进口的电动汽车征收反补贴税，以防止补贴汽车损害欧洲汽车业的风险。我们预计委员会将征收 15-30% 范围内的关税。但即使关税处于这一范围的较高端，一些中国生产商仍然能够在出口到欧洲的汽车上获得可观的利润率，因为他们享有巨大的成本优势。 40-50% 的关税——对于比亚迪这样的垂直一体化制造商来说可能会更高——可能会导致欧洲市场对中国电动汽车出口商失去吸引力。由于不太可能征收这一水平的反补贴税，布鲁塞尔的政策制定者可能会决定转向非传统工具来保护欧洲汽车行业，包括基于环境或国家安全相关因素的限制。</p></blockquote><p>嗯，铑是对的，非关税壁垒——基本上是外国产品无法满足但国内产品可以满足的偷偷制定的法规——在阻止进口方面非常有效。他们认为 40-50% 的关税在欧洲在政治上是不可能的，这也许是对的。但拜登的新关税是荣鼎提到的<em>两倍</em>。这只会摧毁所有中国向美国出口的电动汽车</p><p>现在，用核武器摧毁所有中国对美国的电动汽车出口将对任何人的生活造成基本上<em>零变化</em>。原因是中国目前向美国销售的电动汽车几乎为零： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98e196b0-ca1d-4662-80c6-e48d8f747be2_1477x800.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98e196b0-ca1d-4662-80c6-e48d8f747be2_1477x800.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F98e196b0-ca1d-4662-80c6-e48d8f747be2_1477x800.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-p