s="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>这改变了我对 Twitter 的日常体验——他们经常回复我的推文，而且我在算法中看到了它们。更不祥的是，该平台上的任何讨论现在都容易受到种族主义和反犹太主义内容的垃圾邮件——毫无疑问，其中一些是由无聊的青少年推动的，但其中一些是由总是探索美国社会结构裂缝的俄罗斯账户推动的。</p><p>中国现在也参与了影响力运营游戏。尽管它在直接传播虚假信息方面<a href="https://www.wired.com/story/china-bad-at-disinformation/">不如俄罗斯熟练</a>，但它在控制 TikTok 算法方面拥有极其强大的武器。由于算法源的兴起，社交媒体变得越来越不中介化，能够秘密调整这些算法以抑制或放大某些内容成为信息战的超级大国。</p><p>现在有相当无可争议的<a href="https://networkcontagion.us/wp-content/uploads/A-Tik-Tok-ing-Timebomb_12.21.23.pdf">证据表明</a>，中国积极操纵 TikTok 的算法，以压制它不喜欢的话题。下图显示了 Instagram 和 Tiktok 上主题标签的相对频率 - 对于大多数政治主题，TikTok 的运行率约为 Instagram 的 40%，但对于中国敏感主题，这一比例更像是 1-5%： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg" width="909" height="774" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:774,&quot;width&quot;:909,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:74749,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F4ba99495-3232-4cfd-9392-24291d2e46aa_909x774.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源： <a href="https://networkcontagion.us/wp-content/uploads/A-Tik-Tok-ing-Timebomb_12.21.23.pdf">NCRI/罗格斯大学</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>这主要是对美国人观点的无声审查。美国 TikTok 用户甚至没有意识到这种情况正在发生，因此这不太可能使他们的互联网体验变得更加负面。但随着时间的推移，TikTok 在美国宣扬<a href="https://www.washingtonpost.com/opinions/2024/01/08/china-antisemitism-online-tool-west-gaza/">分裂态度</a>可能会影响人类舆论，使互联网变得比现在更加极端和喧闹。</p><p>当然，总有一些行为者试图在社交媒体上散布虚假信息、影响行动等等——企业、政党、利益集团等等。但中国和俄罗斯政府的资源比任何其他参与者都要好得多——他们有更多的资金、更多的人力和更多的技术致力于这项工作。大男孩们出来玩了，他们改变了我们的互联网，而且通常是变得更糟。</p><h4>斜坡</h4><p>到目前为止，我提到的因素甚至在 ChatGPT 和 Midjourney 以及其他生成式 AI 应用程序的功能爆炸性增长并广泛使用之前就已经存在。现在，生产相当高质量的图像和文本的边际成本已接近于零。因此，人们正在使用生成式人工智能来填充社交媒体……的东西。</p><p>博客<a href="https://www.garbageday.email/">Garbage Day</a>是我最喜欢的跟踪互联网迷因的博客之一（另一个是<a href="https://www.infinitescroll.us/">Infinite Scroll</a> ），有<a href="https://www.garbageday.email/p/internet-looks-like-now">一篇关于这个……东西的好文章</a>。以下是 Facebook 上的一些图片，其中有孩子们驾驶由塑料瓶制成的汽车： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Ffeb42636-54b6-49a8-8e19-c82fb2a1834c_822x476.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto