<div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg" width="608" height="1011.0864745011087" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/d62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1500,&quot;width&quot;:902,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:608,&quot;bytes&quot;:283151,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fd62b46f7-410e-4013-86c1-f01400acd98b_902x1500.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>当然，左派孩子们对此不予赞扬，但左派孩子们很愚蠢。</p><p>基本上，在外交政策上，马蹄铁的两端——MAGA右派的极端分子和“非殖民化”左派——已经<a href="https://twitter.com/MavenNavarro1/status/1785785576571994299">联合起来反对拜登</a>。这是一个强烈的迹象，表明他正在做正确的事情。</p><h4>拜登一直是经济和公共安全的得体管家</h4><p>最后，我们来谈谈影响大多数美国人日常生活的基本问题。经济是许多选民仍然对拜登感到愤怒的问题——两年的实际收入下降会给任何人留下不好的印象。尽管导致通货膨胀的一些因素超出了拜登的控制范围，但正如我之前所说，他的支出可能确实有点加剧了问题。</p><p>但拜登也做了很多事情来帮助平息通货膨胀。首先，也是最重要的是，他重新任命杰罗姆·鲍威尔为美联储主席。许多进步人士担心鲍威尔过于鹰派，加息过多会导致经济衰退。但拜登坚持到底，事实证明这是正确的举动。鲍威尔的加息帮助降低了通货膨胀——虽然没有完全达到 2% 的目标，但足以使实际工资<a href="https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/COMPRNFB">再次开始增长</a>，目前处于大流行前的趋势： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg" width="900" height="535" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:535,&quot;width&quot;:900,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:79038,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F60db6d22-2c26-4605-83cc-3d287d0c87b6_900x535.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div><figcaption class="image-caption">资料来源：<a href="https://twitter.com/arindube/status/1786120315103215861">阿林·杜贝</a></figcaption></figure></div><p>事实上，拜登还做了另一件事来帮助降低通货膨胀：他增加了石油产量。尽管他上任时希望以气候的名义遏制水力压裂，但乌克兰战争却促使他态度大转变。拜登<a href="https://washingtonmonthly.com/2023/03/07/joe-biden-broke-his-2020-pledge-on-fracking-good/">开放了钻探</a>，美国现在生产<a href="https://www.eia.gov/todayinenergy/detail.php?id=61545">的石油比世界历史上任何国家都</a>多。</p><p>更便宜的石油不仅仅使汽油更便宜（尽管它<a href="https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/GASREGW">确实做到了这一点</a>）。它允许各种企业以更便宜的价格运输人员和货物，从而以更便宜的价格生产产品，从而降低通货膨胀。</p><p>因此，拜登做了两件大事来阻止通货膨胀——重新任命鲍威尔，并确保廉价、充足的石油。两人都面对自己政党的压力，表现出了很大的勇气和领导能力。减少医疗保险和学生债务支出本来可以在一定程度上缓解 2021 年的通胀，但拜登在 2022 年和 2023 年降低通胀的行动抵消了这一错误。</p><p>哦，拜登政府还在 2023 年初随心所欲地<a href="https://twitter.com/jessald/status/1761123293942157803">阻止了一场银行业危机。</a>这是一场完美的胜利，几乎没有人记得当时<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-was-there-a-run-on-silicon-valley">的恐慌</a>！</p><p>现在美国经济正全速运转。工资在上涨，增长很快，<a href="https://twitter.com/carlquintanilla/status/1786067237574431145">生产力在增长</a>，年轻人<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/five-things-to-be-optimistic-about">比他们的父辈过得更好</a>，<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/great-news-about-american-wealth">财富增加</a>，就业机会很大，等等。这种金发姑娘的局面不会永远持续下去，但我们需要一些熟练的宏观经济管理才能走到这一步，而拜登和他的政府里的人应该得到一些功劳。</p><p>拜登做对的另一件大事是犯罪。 2020 年，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 领导下的暴力事件激增，许多人担心我们可能会看到 20 世纪 70 年代的情况重演，当时犯罪率在二十多年来一直居高不下。但在拜登的领导下，谋杀率大幅下降： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba047b53-dd90-4a7e-aca0-efa7fc020577_927x517.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba047b53-dd90-4a7e-aca0-efa7fc020577_927x517.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba047b53-dd90-4a7e-aca0-efa7fc020577_927x517.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fba047b53-dd90-4a7e-aca0-efa7fc020