Erik Torenberg 的播客《Econ 102》正在演变成一个问答播客，人们向我提问，我会尽可能快速、信息丰富（并且希望是有趣的）做出回应。如果您有问题希望我回答，您可以通过 Econ102@turpentine.co 将其提交给播客制作人。这是本周的节目，其中包含有关广泛主题的问题： </p><iframe class="spotify-wrap podcast" data-attrs="{&quot;image&quot;:&quot;https://i.scdn.co/image/ab6765630000ba8abc5d6d2fb9a59bcd90652523&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Wealth Distribution, Fixing Healthcare, and UBI&quot;,&quot;subtitle&quot;:&quot;Noah Smith, Erik Torenberg&quot;,&quot;description&quot;:&quot;Episode&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://open.spotify.com/episode/2SfmCYTVbrVB2tPbn9zc8Y&quot;,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;noScroll&quot;:false}" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/episode/2SfmCYTVbrVB2tPbn9zc8Y" frameborder="0" gesture="media" allowfullscreen="true" allow="encrypted-media" data-component-name="Spotify2ToDOM"></iframe><p>不管怎样，进入本周有趣的事情清单吧！</p><h4> 1.中国的国防开支与美国相当</h4><p>在有关国防开支的讨论中，尤其是来自进步人士的讨论中， <a href="https://www.pgpf.org/blog/2024/04/the-united-states-spends-more-on-defense-than-the-next-9-countries-combined">你经常听到的</a>一个话题是，美国的军费开支相当于排在其后 9 个国家的总和。如果你从表面上看这些数字，那就是事实——从纸面上看，美国的支出远远超过其主要竞争对手中国和俄罗斯。 </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg" width="632" height="446.11764705882354" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:720,&quot;width&quot;:1020,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:632,&quot;bytes&quot;:46787,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F83775297-fab2-4b80-86f0-11e5b6bff005_1020x720.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>但讨论的要点是错误的，而且这些数字具有很大的误导性，原因有二。首先，这些数字没有考虑国家之间的相对价格差异；中国士兵的工资、军事装备等的成本比美国低得多，因此中国的性价比要高得多。其次，中国的大量军费开支都是在账面上进行的，所以你在上面的图表中看到的官方数字实际上只是假的。</p><p>当然，反对国防开支的人知道这一点，只是拒绝承认或谈论这一点。但在国防界，每个人都公开谈论这个问题，并且有<a href="https://www.sipri.org/publications/2021/research-reports/new-estimate-chinas-military-expenditure">很多尝试</a>来估计中国在军事上<a href="https://www.iiss.org/en/online-analysis/military-balance/2024/03/chinas-defence-budget-boost-cant-mask-real-pressures/">实际花费了</a>多少。其中许多都考虑了价格差异<em>或</em>预算外支出，但不是两者都考虑在内。美国情报界去年的一项估计将这两件事都考虑在内， <a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/opinion/articles/2023-09-13/china-spends-700-billion-on-its-military-approaching-us-900-billion?sref=R8NfLgwS">得出了 7000 亿美元的数字</a>——几乎与美国的支出一样多。但该方法并未向公众发布。</p><p>现在美国企业研究所已经用非常透明的方法<a href="https://www.aei.org/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/Keeping-Up-with-the-Pacing-Threat-Unveiling-the-True-Size-of-Beijings-Military-Spending.pdf?x85095">进行了自己的分析</a>，他们得出了与情报界发现的非常相似的数字： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg" width="696" height="483.84578313253013" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:577,&quot;width&quot;:830,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:696,&quot;bytes&quot;:87917,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:true,&quot;topImage&quot;:false,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F78376a6c-514a-42d8-bf8f-22bdc5525fcf_830x577.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw" loading="lazy"></picture><div class="image-link-expand"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="lucide lucide-maximize2 "><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"></polyline><polyline points="9 21 3 21 3 15"></polyline><line x1="21" x2="14" y1="3" y2="10"></line><line x1="3" x2="10" y1="21" y2="14"></line></svg></div></div></figure></div><p>你当然可以对这些数字稍加质疑，但大体事实应该很清楚：一旦考虑到价格差异和预算外项目，中国的军费支出与美国的支出大致相同。即使数字有点偏差，仅仅进行这次演习就应该彻底消除美国在国防方面的支出远远超过竞争对手的论点。</p><p> AEI 的分析还显示了美国国防预算中一个巨大的潜在成本节省领域——“运营和维护”。美国在国防上花费如此之多的一个重要原因是我们保持军事<em>活跃</em>。美国军队正在打击海盗，打击随机的当地小恐怖组织，进行各种巡逻，等等——基本上，他们是世界警察。如果我们想将国防开支用于军事现代化和国防工业基础的复兴，我们就必须停止要求我们的军队在日常工作中做这么多事情。</p><h4> 2. 激进的孩子只是新 70 年代的一部分</h4><p>我的“新 1970 年代”论文的一个关键部分是这样的想法：随着大多数美国民众从 2010 年代的动荡中平静下来，铁杆激进分子边缘人士将把那个动荡十年的想法推向更加极端的地步。事实上，轶事表明这种情况正在发生。一小群吵闹但规模较小的<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/palestine-is-the-end-of-the-line">巴勒斯坦抗议者</a>占领了大学校园，而普通人则在关注<a href="https://twitter.com/SwannMarcus89/status/1784761132961481166">更平凡的事情</a>。</p><p>但我们不能仅仅依靠轶事来观察这种分歧；我们还必须依靠轶事来观察这种差异。我们有一些数据。哈佛大学政治学院最近进行的一项<a href="https://iop.harvard.edu/youth-poll/47th-edition-spring-2024#key-takeaway--id--1564">高质量调查</a>（不要与质量较低的哈佛哈里斯民意调查混淆）研究了 18 至 29 岁美国人的观点，发现他们中的大多数人并不认为自己的观点如此高。优先考虑巴勒斯坦或学生债务减免等激进事业。在年轻人的心目中，甚至气候变化也远远落后于通货膨胀、医疗保健和住房等乏味的民生问题： </p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link is-viewable-img image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad6e0b7b-8c30-4549-b96a-8f28fc8da7ad_892x749.jpeg" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad6e0b7b-8c30-4549-b96a-8f28fc8da7ad_892x749.jpeg 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad6e0b7b-8c30-4549-b96a-8f28fc8da7ad_892x749.jpeg 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad6e0b7b-8c30-4549-b96a-8f28fc8da7ad_892x749.jpeg 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad6e0b7b-8c30-4549-b96a-8f28fc8da7ad_892x749.jpeg 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fad6e0b7b-8c30-4549-b96a-8f28fc8da7ad_892x749.jpeg" width="708" height="594.4977578475336" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/ad6e0b7b-8c30-4549-b96a-8f28fc8da7ad_892x749.jpeg&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:749,&quot;width&quot;:892,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:708,&quot;bytes&quot;:160837,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/jpeg&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFo