/figure></div><p>随着利率上升，大流行病储蓄已大部分被花掉，需求驱动型通胀的另一个潜在原因是<a href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/why-is-the-us-doing-so-much-deficit">联邦政府的赤字支出</a>——或者正如高赤字倡导者所称的<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/posts/claudiasahm_big-fiscal-is-a-big-win-for-americans-activity-7168314944201932802-L-4q/">“大财政”</a> 。</p><p>通胀上升通常需要几个月的时间才能渗透到公众舆论中，因此这次通胀的爆发可能不会及时让拜登在 11 月陷入困境。但在通货膨胀加剧之际，政府却参与<a href="https://budgetmodel.wharton.upenn.edu/issues/2022/8/26/biden-student-loan-forgiveness">学生债务减免</a>等大额支出项目，这是在玩一场危险的游戏。 </p><div><hr></div><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"><a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/subscribe?"><span>现在订阅</span></a></p><p class="button-wrapper" data-attrs="{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-3da?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Share&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}" data-component-name="ButtonCreateButton"> <a class="button primary" href="https://www.noahpinion.blog/p/at-least-five-interesting-things-3da?utm_source=substack&utm_medium=email&utm_content=share&action=share"><span>分享</span></a></p><p></p><p></p><p></p>;
